SweatBite
This form is part of a project for our course Human Computer Interaction. 

Help us build a more fun and helpful app about nutrition and fitness!!

All of the answers are anonymous and will help us better understand user needs and design a more useful app. Average time needed to complete is 5 minutes.

Thank you very much for your time!💪🍎
